Add Texture FUZZ       Defualt disturbed   Peened
Right         Left                                         R            L

0.1             0.6                                       1               0
0.2             15                                        1               0.5
0.05            140                                     0.1             90  
0.3               15                                     0.5              90
 
1                  0                                        1
               0
4                  0                                        4
              0.6
0.2                0                                      0.2              1
0.8               0                                      -0.3              0

Cracks
L             R
0            90
0.2         80
0.2          0
15          0
0           0.2
0           0.5
-0.1        0.3
-0.1        0.8

