>On page 301 of my Imagine 3.0 manual, it says "The most common .FLC
>animation format resolutions are PC Lores and PC480." (640x480)
>So I,m assuming that there must be a way. There are plenty of hi-res
>FLC's around to look at and they play fine.  Also the FLC format is
