What?  I called them about their texture docs a while ago to ask if
more docs were coming out about their other interfaces and they said 
yes.  I can't belive they are denying that they wrote it, since they
admitted it to me.  Perhaps you didn't speak to Mike H?  Make sure you
talk to him, as you might be talking to the janitor or something. :)

