I'm replying to you, and to the list, so that everyone may benefit from 
the discussion.

If you have upgraded Imagine since then, remember that Grow is now found 
in the "fx31" directory, not "effects". If you haven't changed the F/X 
Actor bar, it might still point to the old version of the F/X, and that 
could be the key to your problem. Let us know what happens.


